Wayawma yunfakhu fee a<b>l</b><u>ss</u>oori fafaziAAa man fee a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>w<u>a</u>ti waman fee alar<u>d</u>i ill<u>a</u> man sh<u>a</u>a All<u>a</u>hu wakullun atawhu d<u>a</u>khireen<b>a</b>
Watar<u>a</u> aljib<u>a</u>la ta<u>h</u>sabuh<u>a</u> j<u>a</u>midatan wahiya tamurru marra a<b>l</b>ssa<u>ha</u>bi <u>s</u>unAAa All<u>a</u>hi alla<u>th</u>ee atqana kulla shayin innahu khabeerun bim<u>a</u> tafAAaloon<b>a</b>
Man j<u>a</u>a bi<b>a</b>l<u>h</u>asanati falahu khayrun minh<u>a</u> wahum min fazaAAin yawmai<u>th</u>in <u>a</u>minoon<b>a</b>
Waman j<u>a</u>a bi<b>al</b>ssayyiati fakubbat wujoohuhum fee a<b>l</b>nn<u>a</u>ri hal tujzawna ill<u>a</u> m<u>a</u> kuntum taAAmaloon<b>a</b>
Innam<u>a</u> omirtu an aAAbuda rabba h<u>ath</u>ihi albaldati alla<u>th</u>ee <u>h</u>arramah<u>a</u> walahu kullu shayin waomirtu an akoona mina almuslimeen<b>a</b>
Waan atluwa alqur<u>a</u>na famani ihtad<u>a</u> fainnam<u>a</u> yahtadee linafsihi waman <u>d</u>alla faqul innam<u>a</u> an<u>a</u> mina almun<u>th</u>ireen<b>a</b>
